 ('21', '21', 'en_us', 'Diana Nyad: A Look Inside', '', '<p>Legendary long distance swimmer, Diana Nyad, reveals how her inner drive and will to win propelled her in her 100-mile swim from Cuba to Florida. Used as an opening video for a conference, it inspired participants to find their own inner strength to excel and understand that teamwork is critical to success.</p>', '96648957', 'Intel', 'Never Give Up', '0', NULL, '0', '1', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-14 20:45:30', '2015-11-19 21:06:35', 'bce9e4c9-b2c0-46a3-ad9e-e03a9722d56a'),
