 ('25', '25', 'en_us', 'Shooting From The Seat Of Your Pants', NULL, '<p>\r\n	A couple of decades ago, I was part of an agency team pitching a major new project to a very large technology company. In the interest of confidentiality I won’t use their actual name; I’ll just give you their initials&hellip;</p><h1>\r\n	I B M\r\n</h1><p>\r\n	Halfway through our pitch, it was clear we were pretty close to winning the business. In fact, they just had one real concern: were we agile and flexible enough to accommodate their last minute “strategic changes in direction,” (aka: the whims of their senior management team)?</p><p>\r\n	Now this kind of objection is a classic buying signal. It generally means the client is truly interested. One of my colleagues recognized this fact and jumped on it immediately to try and close the deal. I could almost hear the wheels in his mind turning as he worked through two tried-and-true clichés. He later confirmed that what he intended to say was, either:</p><p>\r\n	A) “We’re a company that likes to shoot from the hip&hellip;”</p><p>\r\n	Or&hellip;</p><p>\r\n	B) “We’re a company that likes to fly by the seat of our pants&hellip;”</p><p>\r\n	What he actually said, however, was&hellip;</p><p>\r\n	C) “We’re a company that likes to shoot from the seat of our pants.”</p><p>\r\n	Virtually the same words, right? Entirely different meaning.</p><p>\r\n	NOT a moment of perfect Clarity.</p><p>\r\n	We didn\'t get that job.</p><p>\r\n	Clarity Matters.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'A couple of decades ago, I was part of an agency team pitching a major new project', '0', NULL, '1', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-14 21:43:26', '2014-08-22 22:03:49', 'ab784196-8df3-4c45-b90c-ec4dea9d2dcd'),
 ('26', '26', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, '<h3><strong>Q:</strong>\r\nDoes effective communication begin with the&nbsp;right strategy or the right creative?\r\n</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>A: Yes.</strong></h3>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-14 22:17:53', '2014-08-29 21:06:53', 'df1cf03e-e8f1-43ec-97c4-2e7ca23a43d0'),
 ('27', '27', 'en_us', NULL, 'Clarity Matters', '<p><strong>Clarity</strong> isn’t just the name of our company; it’s our <strong>battle cry</strong>. A one-word <strong>manifesto</strong> defining the fundamental marketing and communications challenge of our time.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-14 22:23:29', '2014-08-29 21:07:05', '115ddf34-46a5-4a47-a3e1-640b6412504a'),
 ('28', '28', 'en_us', NULL, 'Shooting from the seat of your pants', '<p>“Likes,” Links and Learnings on the nature of <strong>clarity</strong> and communications from&nbsp;<strong>Team&nbsp;Clarity</strong>.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-14 22:34:10', '2014-08-29 21:07:19', 'eb65a9aa-4a02-48d8-9efe-0f13a2404df0'),
