 ('30', '30', 'en_us', 'Bill Welter', 'synth seitan', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Founder and Executive Creative Director', '0', '0', '<p>Bill is the founder of Clarity Creative Group and has over 20 years experience in the strategic & creative design and development of corporate communications, presentations and events of all kinds.</p><p>Though he has done work for dozens of Fortune 500 companies, Bill has been engaged primarily with the technology industry for the last decade.  During that time, he has worked closely with senior-level executives and their teams to enhance message effectiveness of high-profile internal and external events and campaigns on a global scale.</p><p>Through their involvement with hundreds of events in nearly 30 countries, Bill and his team have garnered invaluable experience in the best ways to support executive speakers and create fresh, engaging media – often on nearly impossible timelines.</p><p>He formed Clarity Creative Group in 2002 with the goal of providing a new brand of world-class communications strategy and creative execution to a small roster of select clients.</p>', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '2014-08-15 04:56:52', '2014-09-30 15:11:55', '9c0cb35b-22c9-4977-a013-14ea3d8f4162'),
 ('31', '31', 'en_us', 'Gregg Stokes', 'disrupt vegan', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Partner and Executive Art Director', '0', '0', '<p>Gregg has more than 20 years experience in the world of corporate communications and has led creative teams from a variety of positions, including Art Director, Creative Director and Producer.</p><p>As Art Director and then&nbsp;Creative Director for Encore Productions from 1993 – 2002, Gregg was responsible for the overall look and feel of the company’s creative work for clients such as Intel, Microsoft, IBM, John Paul Mitchell, Hewlett-Packard, Toyota, Cadillac, and more.  Throughout he led the visual design process from concept through production while managing multiple creative teams.</p><p>For more than fifteen years, Gregg has partnered with Clarity founder, Bill Welter, designing and producing hundreds of high-profile media and live event projects worldwide for some of the world’s best known and successful companies.  Whether it’s print, video, animation, or motion graphics, Gregg’s visual thinking helps transform complex or mundane messages into easy-to-understand, visually compelling iconography.</p>', '0', '@greggstokes', '3geezy', 'gregg.stokes', 'pub/gregg-stokes/1/750/2b6', '', '0', '2014-08-15 05:07:07', '2014-11-10 04:54:49', '3a3de032-3190-4bf2-8ee0-ba7a7588fe2f'),
 ('32', '32', 'en_us', 'Steven Pine', 'banh mi pour-over', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Partner and Executive Producer', '0', '0', '<p>Steven Pine</p><p>Steven has worked on every side of the creative process for over 25 years, collaborating for the last 15 years with Bill Welter & Gregg Stokes to communicate some of Intel’s most memorable stories and stage their biggest events.  Fusing his directing & production skills; ease with actors & executives alike; and his knowledge of the tech industry, he has produced and directed hundreds of videos and live events for Clarity.</p><p>Prior to Clarity, Steven scratched the acting “itch” in NY and LA, which led to hosting technology trade shows and corporate videos.  He has shared the stage (and camera lens) with some of the tech industry’s biggest names, including Paul Otellini and Andy Grove of Intel. </p><p>As an editor at CNBC, NBC and MSG Networks, Steven honed his skills in the story-telling business, also working as cameraman for NBC focusing on Katie Couric.  These days, his focus is on defining the fundamental marketing & communications challenges at Clarity Creative.</p>', '0', '@Steveninnyc ', '', '', '', '', '0', '2014-08-15 05:07:31', '2014-10-01 16:36:37', '612ef94f-a0f7-471e-b8f7-92603e548140'),
 ('34', '34', 'en_us', 'The Will and the Way', NULL, '<p>\"Where does the computing revolution go from here?”  This was the questioned poised in this opening video produced for a global sales conference.  The answer?  Watch and find out.</p>', '98368819', 'Intel', 'Where does computing go from here?', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-17 20:57:30', '2014-08-27 17:25:01', 'bbb95e51-6e0f-4e3a-a904-19fd42e5dd1a'),
 ('35', '35', 'en_us', '2 in 1 Low Power', NULL, '<p>Introducing Intel\'s revolutionary form factor the \'2 in 1\' featuring the 4th Generation Intel Core Processor with Power Optimizer,  This animated video presents some pretty complex innovation in a simple, easy-to-understand presentation.</p>', '96375750', 'Intel', 'The device that meets all your needs.', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 03:22:40', '2014-08-27 17:24:50', '35fada07-914f-4534-a12f-89f288553c05'),
 ('36', '36', 'en_us', '7 Billion Futures', NULL, '<p>Originally created for a senior executive keynote, this thought-provoking video asks the question, “What\'s the Ultimate Mobile Platform?” Do you know the answer?  (Hint: There are 7 billion of us, and counting&hellip;)</p>', '96373228', 'Intel', 'We are the Network', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2014-08-18 03:40:55', '2014-09-12 18:01:06', '19558443-289a-42f3-bcf4-b1776ef08eb5'),
 ('37', '37', 'en_us', '22nm Atom SoC', NULL, '<p>Great mobile experiences on your tablet or phone begin with what’s \"inside.”  This Explainer video introduces Intel\'s low power, high performance, Intel Atom \'System on Chip\', part of the Intel family of 22nm Atom processors.</p>', '96353605', 'Intel', 'Systems on Chips', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 03:43:21', '2014-08-26 04:31:17', '43647af5-d9cb-4582-bf97-5ecd1eb91e0d'),
 ('38', '38', 'en_us', 'Against All Odds - Ali vs. Forman', NULL, '<p>On October 30, 1974, Ali, described by many as “past his prime” and “over the hill” took on the odds-on favorite, George Forman at the famous ‘Rumble In The Jungle’ in Zaire, Africa.  Who had the ‘Will To Win’?  This video harnessed the emotions and lessons of one of the most famous fights in history to introduce the theme for a global sales conference:  “The Will To Win.”</p>', '97147782', 'Intel', 'The Will to Win', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 03:55:55', '2014-10-01 18:53:33', 'd4838be0-8b7a-448d-a7c2-0df10fc64cb3'),
 ('39', '39', 'en_us', 'Anatomy of a Comeback: The Sean Maloney Story', NULL, '<p>This moving documentary tells the story of Intel executive, Sean Maloney, a dynamic leader & speaker who was poised to become Intel\'s next CEO. Sean suffered a debilitating stroke, paralyzing most of his right side as well as the portion of his brain controlling speech. In this inspiring film, produced by Clarity Creative and narrated by Clarity Founder, Bill Welter, Sean\'s journey is presented and his inspiring comeback recounted.</p>', '97165928', 'Sean Maloney', 'Determination and will make the difference.', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2014-08-18 04:04:24', '2014-09-15 17:39:25', 'a3315a17-6882-4fcc-98f3-555eae803d97'),
 ('40', '40', 'en_us', 'Baytrail Sizzle', NULL, '<p>Description: Set to the classic song, \'Falling In Love Again\', this video uses stunning 3D animation and elegant text graphics to capture the feeling users experience when “falling for” a truly great device.</p>', '96360233', 'Intel', 'Fall in love all over again.', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 04:05:51', '2014-08-26 04:39:51', '375a2355-5017-45c8-acf4-cfcaee62431d'),
 ('41', '41', 'en_us', 'Beamon - Making the Leap', NULL, '<p>This motivational video produced for Paul Otellini\'s keynote at ISMC 2007 tells the story of long jumper Bob Beamon and his record-setting leap into history at the 1968 Olympic Games.</p>', '97150785', 'Intel', 'Shattering Records', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 04:07:22', '2014-08-26 04:45:49', '28762957-dacd-42c5-a85a-d81b0d6cf07f'),
 ('42', '42', 'en_us', 'Brand As Fab', NULL, '<p>Description: This high-powered, music-driven animation leverages a series of on-screen questions to compare the value of the Intel Brand with that of a multi-billion chip fabrication facility.</p>', '96625396', 'Intel', 'What a brand is worth', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 04:13:41', '2014-08-26 04:49:25', '33400db4-2048-4ad5-ba0f-9bb843ad814d'),
 ('43', '43', 'en_us', 'Breaking Barriers', NULL, '<p>The story of Intel is a story of \"barriers broken\" as presented in this compressed look back through the company\'s rich history of innovation, leading it right back to where it is today: the beginning of yet another wave of world-changing progress.  This video originally played as part of an Executive keynote in China.</p>', '97263952', 'Intel', 'A history of innovation', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 04:19:58', '2014-08-26 04:51:16', 'bbe572d1-7cde-408d-86b4-714b94b5aaca'),
 ('44', '44', 'en_us', 'By The Numbers', NULL, '<p>To truly understand the impact of the Intel brand, this video suggests, \"Just do the math.\"  And goes on to do exactly that in a dynamic melding of graphics and music to inspire the 4,000+ attendees at Intel\'s annual sales conference.</p>', '96608682', 'Intel', 'Big Brand Big Numbers', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 04:27:40', '2014-08-26 04:53:03', '16827b05-0874-4925-8e7a-d50d2472fac7'),
 ('45', '45', 'en_us', 'C-RAN - Cloud Radio Access Network', NULL, '<p>This technical video melds 3D graphics to help explain how C-RAN technology helps reduce capital and operating expenses while allowing operators to bring new mobile users online faster and with greater flexibility.</p>', '97259265', 'Intel', 'C-RAN - Cloud Radio Access Network', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 04:52:03', '2014-08-26 04:55:42', '6fdbfdee-e52f-4350-8614-1a6160411a35'),
 ('46', '46', 'en_us', 'Changing the Game', NULL, '<p>This video uses a documentary approach to provide a look back at  the \"The Game that Changed the Game\" - the 1913 Notre Dame vs. Army football contest in which Notre Dame utilized a strategic, innovative game plan featuring the forward pass.  It was “A Game Changer” -- much like the line-up of computing devices presented in this Intel Press Briefing video at CES.</p>', '97252565', 'Intel', 'Innovation moves markets', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 16:47:07', '2014-08-26 04:58:48', '363a03b2-7b93-4254-82dc-b2b418f0fa0c'),
 ('47', '47', 'en_us', 'Consumer Value PC', NULL, '<p>Structured around the question, \"How do you know which PC is best for you?\", this video shows why \"it\'s what inside that counts.”</p>', '96345414', 'Intel', 'How to choose the best PC', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 16:59:27', '2014-08-26 04:59:54', 'e7d08fed-9e66-479b-8b9d-6a11ecaed588'),
 ('48', '48', 'en_us', 'Fashion and Technology', NULL, '<p>The intersection of technology and design is \'Fashion Tech\', and Intel is a leading player in bringing these two worlds together.</p>', '96332666', 'Intel', 'Making wearables desirable ', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 17:06:18', '2014-08-26 05:02:59', '7df97c8b-dc27-4313-892f-76520f8812b6'),
 ('49', '49', 'en_us', 'FUHU and Intel - Learn, Play, Grow', NULL, '<p>Jim Mitchell, CEO of tablet-maker, FUHU discusses the powerful collaboration between his company, Intel, and DreamWorks.</p>', '97755678', 'Intel', 'Tablets and Kids', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 17:21:23', '2014-08-26 05:04:15', 'ff18cbc4-9685-498a-985f-1a5bf9f53df6'),
 ('50', '50', 'en_us', '3D Stone and Tile', NULL, '<p>When revolutionary stone & tile company, 3D Stone and Tile, launched its new line of 3D stone and tile designs, this video presented the technology behind the innovation.</p>', '97865633', '3D Stone and Tile', 'Discover the Magic of 3D', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2014-08-18 17:51:27', '2014-08-31 15:51:53', '630fc46e-a6f2-4652-aa42-fe826971d8fb'),
 ('51', '51', 'en_us', 'High West Distillery and Saloon', NULL, '<p>When boutique whiskey distiller, High West Distillery & Saloon opened its operation in Park City, UT, this video introduced the historic, award-winning company to the public.</p>', '97251534', 'High West Distillery and Saloon', 'Award-winning Whiskey', '0', NULL, '1', '0', NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2014-08-18 17:55:15', '2014-09-16 22:23:35', '4915675e-2bb6-403d-b98f-a9e33c2b1403'),
 ('52', '52', 'en_us', 'Team 4 Tech', NULL, '<p>Team 4 Tech is a non-profit organization that matches volunteer professionals from technology companies with accredited, nonprofit educational organizations to bring much-needed technology and expertise to locations in emerging markets.</p>', '97733733', 'Team 4 Tech', 'Bringing Technology to the World', '0', NULL, '1', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 18:19:54', '2014-08-27 05:21:59', '0577cb93-363a-4c34-b7fa-6259d6435baa'),
 ('53', '53', 'en_us', 'Weil Alumni Event', NULL, '<p>Both executives and alumni of the company, Weil, discuss the importance of staying connected, even after leaving the company as one of their alumni events is documented on this video.</p>', '98139818', 'Weil', 'Staying Connected Has Benefits', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2014-08-18 18:25:29', '2016-08-25 16:48:22', '885af83c-f22f-4fbb-a87a-15ae2bbcbe61'),
 ('54', '54', 'en_us', 'Greensfelder Profile', NULL, '<p>This video profiles a Weil alumni who now works at corporate giant, AIG.  He looks back fondly at his years spent at Weil and discussed how critical those years were to his success as an attorney.</p>', '98139819', 'Weil', 'Reflecting on Success', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2014-08-18 18:28:06', '2014-08-31 20:41:22', 'c4764e55-507a-4e95-b212-478dac6b6885'),
 ('55', '55', 'en_us', 'Saunders a Division of R.S Hughes Co., Inc.', NULL, '<p>An eye-catching, voice-over & 3d graphics-driven introduction to conversion provider, ‘Saunders’ - a division of R.S. Hughes Co., Inc. - a “cut above” the competition.</p>', '97254184', 'R.S. Hughes Co., Inc.', 'A cut above the competition', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2014-08-18 18:30:07', '2014-08-31 18:23:22', '41c9e8f4-d32d-4da3-af70-154a6668b3cb'),
 ('56', '56', 'en_us', 'Hangover - The Grand Entrance', NULL, '<p>Deborah Conrad, Gregory Bryant and Kaz Yoshida have lost SR VP of Sales Tom Kilroy in the desert, and are still trying to find him only minutes before he is to appear on stage at ISMC. CEO Paul Ottellini is clearly not pleased at the news and tells them he expects TK to “Hit that stage in two minutes!”</p>', '97149129', 'Intel', 'It\'s Vegas Baby!', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 18:32:54', '2014-08-26 05:08:27', 'c320986e-01ce-4b41-abfb-ea0b6e473a62'),
 ('57', '57', 'en_us', 'Heroes', NULL, '<p>When Intel needed some “heroic” design wins in the mobile space, the sales force delivered.  Created with a blend of hand-drawn artistry and “After Effects” wizardry, this video made heroes of some of Intel’s best.</p>', '97131027', 'Intel', 'Big Wins need Big Heroes', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 18:36:22', '2014-08-26 05:09:59', '05e451d0-0f6e-4dc0-ac34-5101ae8bc2eb'),
 ('58', '58', 'en_us', 'Intel - Makes Things Faster', NULL, '<p>Shot in a documentary style, consumers are interviewed on city street and asked to talk about their smartphones.  When pressed further regarding how they’d feel about buying a phone with ‘Intel Inside’, the reactions become predictably&hellip; positive.  “Speed, reliability, improved, faster, multi-task flawlessly, and be really cool.”</p>', '97738518', 'Intel', 'How people react to Intel Inside', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 18:40:04', '2014-08-26 05:13:23', 'e0cc3d5f-1a3a-47f6-8437-d0efed55aa0e'),
 ('59', '59', 'en_us', 'Intel® Turbo Boost Technology', NULL, '', '96950388', '', '', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 18:48:44', '2016-08-25 18:40:40', '2ff1c5d7-f959-4282-8d94-25d6643330fb'),
 ('60', '60', 'en_us', 'I Wanna Be Connected', NULL, '<p>The Ramones sang, “I Wanna be Sedated,” but these days, we all want to be connected.  This fun music parody captured that universal feeling as a way to set the tone for a new product launch.</p>', '97145830', 'Intel', 'It\'s Universal', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 18:54:45', '2014-08-26 05:17:54', '6c06ca96-8671-4917-8c9a-3b539f1a6192'),
 ('61', '61', 'en_us', 'Leadership - They Talked, We Listened', NULL, '<p>Intel customers were interviewed across 5 continents and asked to talk about the company and what is can do better to succeed. The answers were as direct and honest as one would expect from business leaders.</p>', '97162980', 'Intel', 'Customers tell the truth', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 19:03:17', '2014-08-26 05:18:46', '327664c7-8e45-48d9-b834-046caa37993e'),
 ('62', '62', 'en_us', 'Lego Mini\'s and Intel - The Power of Partnership', NULL, '<p>A presentation video to the Board of Directors at Lego using children interacting with their tablets in an attempt to sell Lego on the idea that they should allow Intel to create some games/apps designed to take advantage of Intel RealSense technology.</p>', '96333341', 'Intel', 'New Technology expands the game', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-18 19:09:12', '2014-08-26 05:20:46', '2b04a120-76f9-4c00-8103-a64359f28121'),
 ('63', '63', 'en_us', 'Millennials Today', NULL, '<p>When Intel created an ‘Intel Advisory Board’, they solicited some of the youngest, brightest “Millennials” to tell them about how they connect with technology on a daily basis. The results were both dramatic and surprising at once.</p>', '96649551', 'Intel', 'The next great generation', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 14:52:26', '2014-08-26 05:22:58', 'c4edd863-c191-4555-8f4a-518554788032'),
 ('64', '64', 'en_us', 'Mission Critical', NULL, '<p>Technology plays a role in life’s most critical moments. This video explores the hidden complexities that make those moments possible.  After all, when it comes to living our lives, every moment is “mission critical”.</p>', '96952309', 'Intel', 'The magic that happens behind the scenes', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 14:54:25', '2014-08-26 05:23:48', '33f89024-596a-4f4e-b5cf-5f01ac691558'),
 ('65', '65', 'en_us', 'MROI - Marketing Return on Investment', NULL, '<p>Intel’s investment in marketing is a substantial one. So how does a company like Intel possibly quantify such an investment?  By tapping into the voluminous amount of big data and analyzing it to maximize their ROI.</p>', '97536177', 'Intel', 'Big Data Marketing Results', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 14:57:35', '2014-08-26 05:25:25', '7c81d6e7-f359-44b6-a899-1705db030ea3'),
 ('66', '66', 'en_us', 'PC Shopper Journey Part 1 - Traditional Route to Purchase', NULL, '<p>This first part of two videos describes the typical path a consumer follows in the purchase of a PC, and the impact retailers have on this journey.</p>', '97187124', 'Intel', 'How customers decide', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:01:24', '2014-08-27 17:24:14', '044f2f77-b7c3-4607-9f73-4f29ce419c45'),
 ('67', '67', 'en_us', 'PC Shopper Journey Part 2 - The Omni-Channel', NULL, '<p>The traditional PC shopping experience can be a confusing and frustrating one for the consumer at best.  But thanks to ‘The Omni-Channel’, that journey just became a far more seamless and uncomplicated one.</p>', '97187742', 'Intel', 'Shopping made easy', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:02:40', '2014-08-27 17:24:22', 'e859094c-1025-48f6-849b-712b0c3ae11f'),
 ('68', '68', 'en_us', 'Perceptual Computing - Carburetor Repair Day', NULL, '<p>How we interact with our computers is no longer confined to keyboard and mouse. This live action video shows how some of our not so distance future interactions will happen, using hand gestures and and voice control. &nbsp;</p>', '96642529', '', '', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:04:13', '2014-08-19 23:48:06', '44bdfb95-1205-4105-bf07-739009681b0d'),
 ('69', '69', 'en_us', 'Peter Diamandis and Moores Law', NULL, '<p>The CEO & Founder of XPrize Foundation, Peter Diamandis, traces the startling advances and innovations in technology back to Moore’s Law.  “We are pushing the edge of knowledge every single day,” he affirms, providing a unique POV on the current state of innovation and technology.</p>', '96821342', 'Intel', 'Technology changes everything', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:07:18', '2014-08-26 05:31:03', '9e960b7e-be59-44e2-8b1f-e4d3d5e657a8'),
 ('70', '70', 'en_us', 'Potential', NULL, '<p>Leveraging the power of After Effects to create a 3D effect with still photos, this keynote opener examines the driving force common to humans around the planet: the desire to achieve our full potential.</p>', '96954384', 'Intel', 'It is inside us all', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:09:32', '2014-08-26 05:31:49', '54549fe0-6974-4d4a-a6fa-04eba493e1a7'),
 ('71', '71', 'en_us', 'Questions', NULL, '<p>This video served as the opening for Paul Otellini’s 2010 IDF speech.  It set the stage for his ‘Beyond the PC’ vision by reminding us of all the ways the microprocessor and PC have already changed the world, while pointing towards a future in which the microprocessor comes “out of the box” and into an array of new and innovative devices.</p>', '97143255', 'Intel', 'How to change the world', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:11:35', '2014-08-26 05:33:21', 'a0162f55-d173-4fc5-907b-2b9066838929'),
 ('72', '72', 'en_us', 'Road to Wonderful - Look Inside', NULL, '<p>Where does the road to wonderful start?  With something “Inside”... as this inspirational video melding what’s inside technology with what’s inside each of us; simply, something wonderful.</p>', '96373710', 'Intel', 'It begins with you', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:12:54', '2014-08-26 05:37:49', '7eb26058-0c16-43eb-a390-b78997cb8342'),
 ('73', '73', 'en_us', 'Scaling New Heights', NULL, '<p>Produced with the goal of motivating a global sales force, this contemporary, graphics-driven approach asks a classic question: What are the steps the modern day consumer takes during the purchase journey?  Melding 3-D motion graphics with Morgan Freeman’s memorable voice-over, this video was the first in a series examining this most important issue, as Intel faced a difficult year ahead.  This video tells the story of how Sir Edmund Hillary and Tenzing Norgay battling immense odds to become the first men in history to summit Mt. Everest.<strong></strong></p>', '97152003', 'Intel', 'Against all odds', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:14:37', '2014-08-26 05:41:56', 'c88d514b-29e8-48f1-9de4-1e9f59518a59'),
 ('74', '74', 'en_us', 'Tech Chef - Choosing the Right Processor', NULL, '<p>An Intel Techy travels the US in his ‘tech truck’ answering peoples vexing questions about PCs, 2in1s and other computing devices.</p>', '97139191', 'Intel', 'Serving Up Information', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:17:58', '2014-08-26 05:46:15', 'b43b5065-a1f5-4358-adad-40a700c690e5'),
 ('75', '75', 'en_us', 'Tech Chef - Different Types of Ultrabook Convertibles', NULL, '<p>An Intel “Techy” travels the US in his unique “tech truck” answering consumers’ vexing questions about PCs, 2-in-1s and other form factors and computing devices.</p>', '97141242', 'Intel', 'You need answers? We\'ve got them.', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:20:06', '2014-08-26 05:47:12', '3a58dab2-d93f-49e1-b8ea-cd0e0b0e8ca4'),
 ('76', '76', 'en_us', 'The Amazing Tri-Gate Transistor - 22nm Launch', NULL, '<p>An Intel ‘Senior Fellow’ presents for the viewer some interesting facts about the remarkable transistors that comprise the microprocessors made by Intel; including the fact that they continue to get smaller, faster, and now, even 3D - thanks to Moore’s Law.</p>', '96935869', 'Intel', 'Extending Moores Law', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:23:29', '2014-08-26 05:49:37', '5b73ac2d-d4fe-41e7-b716-835ea42cf517'),
 ('77', '77', 'en_us', 'The Beginning', NULL, '<p>It’s been 30 years since the introduction of the ‘IBM 5150’, but as this inspirational video shows us - thanks to Moore’s Law - those 30 years have seen unprecedented change year after year, leading up to today.  The Beginning.</p>', '96819434', 'Intel', 'It all started over 30 years ago.', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:24:33', '2014-08-26 05:49:16', 'eaf47cc8-f7ff-4621-b2ee-3e967fd739c3'),
 ('78', '78', 'en_us', 'The Places We’ll Go', NULL, '<p>In the age of computerized everything, this retro, hand-drawn animation stood out as something special at the last Intel Developer’s Forum.  A good-natured illustration of where Intel’s Atom chip is heading, this video turned out to be just was the Dr. (Seuss, that is) ordered.</p>', '98142824', 'Intel', 'The Magic of The Intel® Atom™ processor', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:26:09', '2016-08-25 16:43:58', 'fcefaa57-5e67-4e49-8994-517fe0f0d7cf'),
 ('79', '79', 'en_us', 'The Power of Small - Bringing 22mn to Mainstream Computing', NULL, '<p>One of Intel’s ‘Senior Fellows’ returns to bring the viewer up to date on the state of Intel’s latest (and smallest) 3D transistors yet - together with a co-worker, they take a ‘Fantastic Voyage’ to 3rd Generation Core and the latest Quad Core microprocessor.</p>', '97133700', 'Intel', 'Journey inside a microprocessor', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:28:31', '2014-08-28 22:50:05', '9c839e58-5cd1-463c-bd7c-f954426e0a00'),
 ('80', '80', 'en_us', 'The Revolution will be Digitized', NULL, '<p>This tongue-in-cheek, graphics-driven video is a spoof of the famous 1970\'s tone poem, ‘The Revolution Will Not Be Televised.’  It was produced as an opener for an executive keynote examining the future of technology.</p>', '97144404', 'Intel', 'The future of Technology', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:30:25', '2014-08-26 05:58:55', '6166d8bb-2216-42d2-b91b-9ad426f0b27b'),
 ('81', '81', 'en_us', 'The Secret Lives of Shoppers', NULL, '<p>Shoppers - we know they’re on the move, but what’s going to “inside” the shopper’s mind?  This video presents some up to date and eye-opening facts about just what shoppers do, what they want, and who they truly are.</p>', '96281334', 'Intel', 'New ways to view customers', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:31:45', '2014-08-26 06:01:28', 'd70cded8-7d18-41c7-be43-afdaf2187a7c'),
 ('82', '82', 'en_us', 'This is the Future', NULL, '<p>This inspiring keynote video for a global sales convention presents, without a word spoken, a video about our “future in the making” and all the wonders of technology it will encompass.</p>', '96818793', 'Intel', 'The wonders of technology', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:34:37', '2014-08-26 06:02:40', 'ce8b51b5-48c3-48d3-969a-7f3b732d07e2'),
 ('83', '83', 'en_us', 'Transistors: Small Wonders. Big Numbers.', NULL, '<p>This animation-intensive video produced for Intel’s Investor Relations team compares the number of ants on earth to the number of transistors.  It helps explain why the exponential growth in transistor demand is destined to continue for decades to come.</p>', '96950715', 'Intel', 'MIPS make the world', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-19 15:35:52', '2014-08-26 06:04:44', '5c49d43a-c09b-4908-954d-7d9bf91f03ac'),
 ('84', '84', 'en_us', 'Walmart Mom  - 2nd Generation Intel® Core™ Processors', NULL, '<p>Produced for the express purpose of playing on computer screens at Walmart stores throughout the United States, this video seamlessly combines hand-drawn animation with live action actors to show why PC’s with Intel processors inside are the “right choice” for consumers on a shopping journey.<strong></strong></p>', '96864596', 'Intel', 'The right choice for you', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2014-08-19 15:37:56', '2014-08-31 15:54:33', '5043097f-459b-41d8-9a03-72d327f6b3c9'),
 ('85', '85', 'en_us', 'What Type of Computer User Are You?', NULL, '<p>This video identifies the three main types of computer users, and asks the viewer, “Which one are you?”  Basic?  Everyday? Or Performance?  Whichever one you are, OfficeMax can help you find the right computer for you.</p>', '96959792', 'Office Max', 'Find out now.', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2014-08-19 15:39:14', '2014-08-31 18:22:53', 'e13b4d57-0c34-4b71-a4ad-c23f37ae9a02'),
