 ('105', '105', 'en_us', 'Gameloft', NULL, '<p>An exciting, eye-catching video, the melding of motion graphics and interview come together to take a look at how game designer, ‘Gameloft’, partners with intel to create the digital platforms necessary to create breakthrough video games.</p>', '103930838', 'Intel', 'Making Breakthrough Video Games', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-20 18:43:02', '2014-08-26 05:05:12', '4ea77834-dc15-407c-ac0b-7dd6d1b92495'),
 ('106', '106', 'en_us', 'Behind the Scenes of AnandTech with Anand Shimpi', NULL, '<p>A spoof video featuring celebrity tech reviewer, Anand Shimpi, this video played just before Anand took the stage at Intel’s annual ISMC convention, poking fun at his reviewing “techniques”.</p>', '103918248', 'Intel', 'A fun look at product reviews', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-20 18:45:27', '2014-09-07 00:26:34', '519e5ce5-fc43-4b39-a6dd-53e1f8957ca5'),
 ('107', '107', 'en_us', 'The Bridge', NULL, '<p>The story of “the bridge that&nbsp;couldn\'t&nbsp;be built” - the Golden Gate Bridge is a story of a dream that had to be pursued;&nbsp;and in the end, an example of how when we have the will&hellip; we find the way.</p>', '103911363', 'Intel', 'Finding a way to make things happen.', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-20 18:47:22', '2014-08-26 05:53:00', '7024d23d-7395-4818-8203-10e682a3bd3a'),
 ('112', '112', 'en_us', 'Peter Smaha', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Writer and Creative Director', '0', '0', '<p>Peter joins Clarity after 20+ years as a  Creative Director/Writer/Director.  His background includes 10+ years of  Madison Avenue advertising with Saatchi-Saatchi, as well as forming his  own agency, Quigley-Simpson, to service primarily various Proctor &  Gamble brands.  Additionally, Peter has been a  freelance speechwriter for high profile/celebrity speakers and a  creative director/branding consultant across various media.</p>', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '2014-08-22 01:49:21', '2014-09-08 03:09:27', 'b8a01a4f-6ce7-4ae8-aed6-d081a05c4283'),
