 ('118', '118', 'en_us', 'Intel Ambassador visits Dreamworks', NULL, '<p>We meet Nhu, an Intel Manufacturing Supervisor working for Intel, Vietnam as she provides a perspective on not only working at Intel but also being an Ambassador for Intel, a program that allowed her to visit Dreamworks in CA.</p>', '104113244', 'Intel', 'Life long dream comes true', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 17:34:31', '2014-08-27 16:50:25', '7d8f666e-e4c0-4d54-bedf-97473c9cd87a'),
