 ('121', '121', 'en_us', 'Brand Trust Spans All Devices', NULL, '<p>David Ginsberg, Intel’s Director of Insights & Market Research, affirms the consumer belief that if given the choice, they’d prefer a smartphone with ‘Intel Inside’... all you have to do is ask them.</p>', '104126578', 'Intel', 'Global Worldwide Research', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 19:23:48', '2014-08-27 16:50:35', 'ffe32214-b818-4a03-a3bd-6f67333e2ff9'),
 ('122', '122', 'en_us', 'Secretariat - The Heart of a Champion', NULL, '<p>What truly makes a champion? In this inspiring video played before the gathered Intel ISMC audience, the remarkable story of Secretariat - the greatest race horse who ever lived - is recounted.  And it just so happens, he truly had the “heart of a champion.”</p>', '104133516', 'Intel', 'The Greatest Race Horse Ever', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 19:56:22', '2014-08-27 16:51:25', '4a48f44b-a8a8-4143-959a-a58d2782a208'),
 ('123', '123', 'en_us', 'The Science of Understanding Your Customer', NULL, '<p>This video explores how Neuroscience and Cognitive Psychology help Intel gain insights into the non-conscious reactions to technology.  Numerous experts in the field discuss the processes their companies follows to better understand the vast complexities of the human brain; as David Ginsberg from Intel talks about how Intel utilizes this information.</p>', '104135682', 'Intel', 'Neuroscience and Cognitive Psychology ', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 20:33:51', '2014-08-27 16:50:40', '1297df12-60d4-47e3-8a00-2c70a9ebb23e');
