 ('124', '124', 'en_us', 'Baby Ravi Talks IT', NULL, '<p>Inspired by the popular ‘etrade’ ad campaign featuring talking “babies,” we meet Baby Ravi from Intel who presents a new line of products as well as the Intel IT Center to fellow Intel staffers.</p>', '104139021', 'Intel', 'Intel IT Centers ready to Scale', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 21:29:30', '2014-08-27 16:50:20', '9f9e0aa6-d3ea-4a17-b5c2-887d6c375ef5'),
 ('125', '125', 'en_us', 'Silicon', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 21:41:53', '2016-10-18 16:10:28', '83622bfa-1875-4fc7-b20a-50c291edfb3e'),
 ('126', '126', 'en_us', 'Intel Silicon Photonics', NULL, '<p>This video asks the viewer to “imagine a future where data runs through the data center as well as devices at the speed of light.”  The integrated solution?  Intel Silicon Photonics.</p>', '104143319', 'Intel', 'Moving at the speed of light', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 21:42:59', '2014-08-27 16:50:29', '9b2db2db-5718-4e7a-820d-3f27217e9214'),
 ('127', '127', 'en_us', 'Camp e-Otter', NULL, '<p>A parody of the famous Allan Sherman song, ‘Camp Grenada’, campers sing, “Hello Muddah, Hello Faddah” from their e-camp which features the latest in technology and devices.</p>', '104144158', 'Intel', 'Kids and Technology', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 21:55:46', '2014-08-27 16:50:15', '18025f10-4420-4812-a7a1-443b5bac2160'),
 ('128', '128', 'en_us', 'Perceptual Computing - Capturing the World', NULL, '<p>In an interview with Mark Yahiro, Managing Director, New Business for Perceptual Computing at Intel, the interaction between devices and users is explored; specifically, capturing the world of children&hellip; for children.</p>', '104146123', 'Intel', 'Interpreting Gestures', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 22:24:30', '2014-08-27 16:49:14', '7ca0b473-1722-4d52-a331-e93575e94ad3'),
 ('129', '129', 'en_us', 'Leehom and his super cool Ultrabook™ ', NULL, '<p>Set to the classic songs, ‘Falling in Love Again,’ we meet “Leehom” as he uses his super cool new Ultrabook Convertible in Japan&hellip; a device that attracts quite a bit of attention as it changes form factors right before our eyes.</p>', '104146729', 'Intel', 'You never know who the superstar is.', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 22:40:45', '2014-08-27 16:49:04', '458b8139-c5ae-4561-ba49-416c16ea64a4'),
