 ('131', '131', 'en_us', 'Making a Better World Possible', NULL, '<p>“The way we see it, everyone deserves to be connected” is the theme of this inspiring video, with connectivity extending beyond our devices, to our passions and potential.</p>', '104147755', 'Intel', 'Technology helps people do amazing things', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-08-22 22:54:57', '2014-08-27 16:48:53', '7ee3bc85-6f7c-44ce-bd5c-122df3aecaa3'),
