 ('185', '185', 'en_us', 'Video Example', NULL, '<p>Pinterest Thundercats retro, mustache fingerstache salvia freegan Helvetica fashion axe twee chia banh mi kogi. Wolf fixie skateboard, Thundercats dreamcatcher next level pug letterpress vinyl keffiyeh art party mustache beard. Small batch messenger bag single-origin coffee direct trade Thundercats, pop-up aesthetic 3 wolf moon twee readymade sriracha mixtape. Bespoke craft beer meh selvage YOLO. Blue Bottle meggings kogi, irony cornhole actually Godard post-ironic trust fund. Street art cliche fashion axe small batch. Small batch 90\'s sriracha, wayfarers Marfa keytar brunch.</p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/76874277\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe><p><a href=\"http://vimeo.com/76874277\">THE WES ANDERSON COLLECTION CHAPTER 1: BOTTLE ROCKET</a> from <a href=\"http://vimeo.com/rogerebert\">RogerEbert.com</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p><p>Yr ethical four loko, disrupt narwhal try-hard Brooklyn aesthetic. Intelligentsia stumptown Pitchfork distillery aesthetic biodiesel Marfa, put a bird on it Carles mustache artisan church-key fap typewriter whatever. Odd Future 8-bit bicycle rights squid master cleanse occupy DIY, mixtape cornhole freegan single-origin coffee aesthetic. Meh viral VHS, Odd Future Austin cornhole flannel wolf Pitchfork Intelligentsia fap four loko street art. Quinoa polaroid Etsy, blog swag kale chips cred irony mlkshk Shoreditch flexitarian cornhole wolf sriracha. High Life freegan next level pour-over. Banjo High Life roof party fingerstache, trust fund iPhone meggings actually tote bag dreamcatcher messenger bag umami.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'This is and example of a video post', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-09-02 18:24:13', '2014-09-02 18:24:21', 'adc75614-62fa-414c-9069-f25a6f6d1596'),
 ('186', '186', 'en_us', NULL, 'Develop', '<p>Ready. Fire. Aim. Why do so many corporate communication efforts seem to have been launched before the target they were meant for has been clearly identified and located? We know why: because someone didn’t take the time to ask the right questions. We ask the right questions.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-09-03 03:20:55', '2014-09-06 16:28:30', 'ef3c2823-a022-4ab6-8e9b-f15de1b48da3'),
 ('187', '187', 'en_us', NULL, 'Design', '<p>We are living in the Golden Age of video; It’s never been easier or more cost-effective to produce and distribute great, high-impact video; which also means it’s never been easier to produce and distribute bad, no-impact video.</p><p>Most production companies “make” videos; at Clarity, we “design” videos. This seemingly small distinction makes all the difference. Want to know more about our design-centered approach? Give us a call. We can talk about it all day.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-09-03 03:21:25', '2014-09-06 16:28:11', 'd9d02765-ab43-462f-b165-ff085f580588'),
 ('188', '188', 'en_us', NULL, 'Deliver', '<p>“You guys know how to get sh*t done!”</p><p>Can there be any higher praise from a client/friend/partner? We don’t think so.</p><p>Not in the constantly churning waters of our 24/7 digital world. Sometimes the success of a project is determined first and foremost by getting it done on a schedule others thought was impossible.</p><p>With more than 15 years experience producing videos in more than 30 countries, we’ve developed a network of production super heroes that would put The Avengers to shame. Got an impossible deadline? Bring it on.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2014-09-03 03:21:55', '2014-09-06 16:28:52', '29a1f1b9-ba1f-422c-9d9a-1a9d520e87fb'),
