 ('223', '223', 'en_us', 'Dona Shatford Peters', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Senior Producer', '0', '0', '<p>After more than 10 years in broadcast television production of live music concert specials, dance/fashion events and drama series, Dona‘s experience as a Line Producer, Producer and Executive Producer led to a Partnership with a Film & Television Development Company. Her skills in scripting and packaging projects moved her into the Production of Music Videos, Cable Commercials, and Convention Videos for Corporate Executives.</p><p>Working with Bill Welter for the past 15 years, Dona has produced hundreds of Keynote Videos: Testimonials, Music Video Parodies and Openers for clientele including IBM, EMC and Intel. Her past experience has provided her with the skills to take on any Media Project, which she has produced with Clarity Creative’s well known sense of humor, speedy delivery, and exceptional quality.</p>', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '2015-02-24 03:45:51', '2015-03-18 15:11:26', 'cf960166-45cb-4a3a-8ba1-574de82c7b8e'),
