 ('229', '229', 'en_us', 'Angie Sperrazza', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Senior Producer & Production Coordinator', '0', '0', '<p>Angie Sperrazza joins the Clarity team as a highly sought-after Associate Producer and Production Coordinator.  Her wide-ranging skills both in live event and video production have served such companies as Intel, Kia Motors, Google, Samsung, The Home Depot, Skype, and many more.</p><p>Before stepping into the live show arena, Angie was an Operations Manager leading multiple teams of post-production professionals in assignments including live action and animation videos, broadcast commercials, and videos across a range of subjects.  She has also coordinated productions globally across 5 continents for various corporate videos and international documentaries.  Angie’s unique skill sets will be applied across the full range of Clarity projects, and we’re delighted to welcome her to the team.</p>', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '0', '2016-02-18 19:09:36', '2016-02-23 22:03:45', '7550dc29-2b0f-46f6-9047-b0c19e6e562f'),
