 ('231', '231', 'en_us', 'The Butterfly Effect', NULL, '<p>In the Butterfly Effect, we explain how in&nbsp;networked systems and organizations, even small changes can dramatically transform the whole.&nbsp;</p>', '132135395', 'Intel', 'Small Changes Big Results', '0', NULL, '1', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2016-08-25 16:26:11', '2016-08-26 16:00:00', 'e6d446d5-b48d-443a-bceb-cb6e4a2de8ac'),
 ('232', '232', 'en_us', 'This is NOW!', NULL, '<p>This 3D animation featuring the latest computer&nbsp;technology and form factors&nbsp;proves there has never been a better time to buy a PC.&nbsp;</p>', '180208451', 'Intel', 'This is Now', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-08-25 18:40:10', '2016-08-26 16:00:34', 'b17d008c-2311-4a68-86c6-654aff50a1c0'),
 ('233', '233', 'en_us', 'Good to be Alive', NULL, '<p>An exciting new era of possibilities for businesses everywhere to expand and have access to new sources of revenue and growth.</p>', '180219176', 'Intel', 'Good to be Alive', '1', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-08-25 19:44:37', '2016-08-26 16:00:46', '2f9a00b9-0274-403f-8e31-a6fb8baf9077'),
 ('234', '234', 'en_us', 'Speed of Life', NULL, '<p>Billions of connected devices will demand a flexible and powerful 5G network.</p>', '180217676', 'Intel', 'Speed of Life', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '2016-08-25 20:10:33', '2016-08-25 20:11:24', '9d79805a-b847-4d6b-96da-30938667d2a5'),
 ('236', '236', 'en_us', 'The Magic of RealSense', NULL, '<p>Explore how your world becomes more interesting because your camera can see. This splash screen animation  takes you to an imaginary world where you can selectively wipe away images to reveal a magical world.</p>', '180226365', 'Intel', 'The Magic of RealSense', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-08-26 18:48:00', '2016-08-26 18:48:00', 'b7999efa-66b5-481c-aeb4-838c089b6c19'),
 ('237', '237', 'en_us', 'Best Days of Your Life', NULL, '<p>Nothing is better than kids and computers. With RealSense Technology and entire new level of interactivity can be experienced.</p>', '180230185', 'Intel', 'RealSense Technology creates new experiences', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-08-26 18:58:38', '2016-08-26 18:58:38', '0d85f3cc-7bf5-4d60-a5bf-771db03b30db'),
 ('238', '238', 'en_us', 'Speed Shift', NULL, '<p>Explore the concept of Speed Shift technology where the hardware anticipates user needs based on history. This allows for a snappier more responsive feel and helps save power. The processor has been designed in a way that with the right commands, the OS can hand control of the frequency and voltage back to the processor. Intel is calling this technology \'Speed Shift\'.</p>', '180232761', 'Intel', 'Speed Shift', '0', NULL, '0', '0', NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-08-26 19:06:47', '2016-08-26 19:06:47', 'f63692fe-780c-4b80-8dd8-b9197a058233');
