 ('442', '30', '6', '1', 'en_us', '14', '', '{\"typeId\":\"6\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Bill Welter\",\"slug\":\"bill-welter\",\"postDate\":1408730400,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"16\":\"<p>Bill is the founder of Clarity Creative Group and has nearly 20 years of experience in the strategic and creative design and development of corporate communications, presentations and events of all kinds.&lt;br&gt;<\\/p><p>The firm\\u2019s name reflects Bill\\u2019s personal philosophy that effective communication is based on the difficult challenge of finding just the right balance between the message and the mechanism by which it is delivered; between the substance and the sizzle; between creativity and&hellip;clarity. When perfect balance is achieved, the result is clear, impactful, effective communication.<\\/p><p>Though he has done work for dozens of Fortune 500 companies, Bill has been engaged primarily with Intel Corporation for the last five years. During that time, he has worked closely with many of the company\\u2019s senior-most executives and their teams to enhance message effectiveness of high-profile internal and external events around the world.<\\/p><p>As Vice President of Creative Services at Encore Productions from 1995 - 2001, Bill created and managed a team that operated as a company-within-the-company dedicated exclusively to serving Intel\\u2019s creative production needs worldwide. Through their involvement with more than 100 Intel events in nearly 30 countries, Bill, and the core creative team he works with, has garnered invaluable experience in the best ways to support executive speakers and create compelling, easy-to-customize media.<\\/p><p>Bill holds dual graduate degrees in Creative Writing and Film\\/Video Production as well as undergraduate degrees in English and Business. He has personally served as Creative Director and\\/or Executive Producer on more than 300 high-profile corporate videos and events.<\\/p><p>In early 2002, he formed Clarity Creative Group with the goal of providing a new brand of world-class communications strategy and creative execution to a small roster of select clients.<\\/p>\",\"11\":[\"182\"],\"12\":\"Founder | Executive Creative Director\",\"9\":[\"142\"]}}', '2014-08-29 06:30:40', '2014-08-29 06:30:40', '3feea31b-0b2f-491c-94f0-8cc6d94be5bb'),
